com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool

Class CycInspectorTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.AbstractKbTool
      • com.cyc.baseclient.kbtool.CycInspectorTool
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InspectorTool

    public class CycInspectorTool
extends AbstractKbTool
implements InspectorTool
    Tools for examining individual CycObjects. To examine the relationship between different CycObjects, use the CycComparisonTool.
    See Also:
    CycComparisonTool
